step_description: You are importing the good for any of the following purposes:
step_howto_description: Trade samples, laboratory samples or as display items for exhibitions, which are not intended to be placed on the market; consignments of food and feed which form part of passengers personal luggage and are intended for personal consumption or use; non-commercial consignments of food and feed sent to natural persons which are not intended to be placed on the market; consignments of food and feed intended for scientific purposes.
